      • buildGitUri

        public GitUri buildGitUri(URI uri)
                   throws IOException,
                          URISyntaxException
        Builds a GitUri from a GitHub Pages URL. It performs a DNS lookup for the CNAME if the host does not match GITHUB_PAGES_HOST_PATTERN. Builds the wagon specific Git URI based on the repository URL. This is made public rather than protected to allow testing of the method.
